	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Gratia filii dei tecum.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Ne mirere, doctissime <persName ref="p495">Bullingere</persName>, meum diuturnum silentium, ne dicam, quod te non reddiderim certiorem, an is quem tuis literis domine commendaras, posset abeunti succedere <persName ref="p8071">Voglero</persName>.<note type="margin">a.R.: <persName ref="p8071">Joh.Vogler</persName> von 1562–67 Schaffner in <placeName ref="l404">Rappoltsweiler</placeName></note></s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">At <persName ref="p20051">Vertumnus</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Gott des steten Wandels; vgl. <bibl>Adagia</bibl>, 2, 2, 74 (<bibl>LB</bibl> II 473).</note> ille noster ex uno ore calidum et frigidum spirans responsum distulit, neque <persName ref="p8071">Voglerus</persName> suum abdicabit munus, tametsi dicat se sub autumno paraturum discessum.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Hodie tibi scripturus rursum scripsi domine; sed ex inserta schedula intelliges negotium; ita arridet illi lucellum etc.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Ecclesiola nostra lente festinat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l411">Richenvillę</placeName> regnant ubiquiste magna ecclesię iactura<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">a.R.: nach Erbs Vertreibung 1560/61</note>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Legisti, opinor, <persName>Palatinorum</persName> responsa in <placeName>Farczbachium</placeName><note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">a.R.: =Marbach?</note> (ut vocant).</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Non cessat <persName>Stentor</persName> pro rostris ad raucim / ranzim usque clamare; sed maior pars <placeName ref="l491">Argentorat[ensium]</placeName> nauseant eius calumnias.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Magistratus caute agens metuit, ne turba excitetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Conventus principum in ianuario futurus est; quid decernent, dies declarabit.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">Ingens spes <placeName ref="l452">Selestad</placeName>, <placeName ref="l101">Colmariensem</placeName> et reliquas civitates decem, quę domui <placeName ref="l850">Austriacę</placeName> obpignoratę sunt, Christum recepturas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la">Haganoa, quae primaria est, exactis sacrificis concionatorem substituerunt quam sequentur et [...] <placeName>Obernehenen</placeName>, <placeName ref="l101">Colmarię</placeName> totus senatus conspirarunt in Christum, excepto uno et altero.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la">Oramus strenue ut Christi regnum propagetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la">Et vos orate pro nobis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la">Raptim die sali [...] anno Christi natalitium 1565.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la">Tuus <persName ref="p1010">Matthias Erbius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la">Incomparabili viro pietate ac eruditione d. <persName ref="p495">Henricho Bullingero</persName>, ecclesię <placeName ref="l587">Tigurinę</placeName> theologo atque antistiti fidelissimo, suo fratri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
